===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''alpha taxonomy'''
#{{taxonomy}} the science of finding, describing, classifying and naming living things.

Usage: a [[retronym]], this is used in those cases where the word [[taxonomy]] may be ambiguous:
* where the word [[taxonomy]] is (also) used in the sense of a classification in a hierarchical system.
* where the word [[systematics]] is used in the sense of [[cladistically]] evaluating DNA-data only.